Another map i made, now its cold, rainy and warm in the sauna. 
 
You can go straight in to sauna and blow it up, or u can blow up the dam what is keeping additional rain water out side of the map and extinguish the fire from the sauna. 
And counter-terrorists have to prevent terrorists from ruin their nice vacation in the rainy forest.
 
I didnt find any bugs or anything other unnecessary things from the map, if u find any please tell me about them :). 
 
And patosauna means damsauna in english if some1 want to know.
